Help > Check for Appcelerator updates is working fine in our  environment .

[~binho] Please try the following steps :

To Install the Appcelerator Command Line Tools (CLI) , do so from the command line:
{code}
sudo npm install appcelerator -g
{code}
To install the Latest version SDK, do so from the command line:
{code}
appc ti sdk install -d 4.1.0.v20150626223333
or
appc ti sdk install (SDK version )
{code}

Thanks
